Experience with object-oriented software design and service-oriented architectures;
Experience with responsive design a plus;
Experience with SQL database a plus;
Ability to work well with others;
Able to meet deadlines and multitask;
Effective verbal and written communication skills with both technical and non-technical audience;
Ability to work under pressure and manage multiple priorities.
Fluent in French and English (spoken and written);


